{"tid":2196344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國稱反華分子惡意攻擊劉曉明 Twitter 以讚好色情內容","createTime":"2020-09-09T23:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T00:54:11.000Z","uid":348984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37766a86becd634b754e53250693b867d82ed674","tid":2196344,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:18:07.000Z","msg":"中國駐英大使劉曉明的社交網站賬號讚好色情內容，大使館指責有反華分子惡意攻擊他的賬號。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明的 Twitter 戶口星期三讚好了一段長 10 秒的色情影片，片段發送者的其他推文，全部為簡體中文的色情內容。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐英大使館的聲明並未承認或否認確有此事，但稱有「個別反華分子通過網絡惡意攻擊」劉曉明的 Twitter，「大肆惡搞，手段卑劣」，大使館嚴厲譴責，並向 Twitter 檢舉這種行為，敦促 Twitter 認真調查、嚴肅處理。英文版聲明對「攻擊」的描述為「attack」。劉曉明轉發了聲明，表示「真金不怕洪爐火」。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 方面目前尚未回應事件。而劉曉明的賬戶所讚好的推文，已由之前的 50 條，減至現時的 2 條，2 條推文均來自他的賬號。"},{"pid":"903f300cf96cf12d3588900341c8f0ca20317390","tid":2196344,"uid":348984,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HhXcJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HhXcJg.jpg&h=3b4aa1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3081132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3081132&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=28ac8636\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3081132&h=ba382f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3081132</a>"},{"pid":"cab6f08fda97a9597a3bf3c4ee608142df11a41e","tid":2196344,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"邊個hack我"},{"pid":"cd82239951f5c9af10063f248bd81be6df5c1ea8","tid":2196344,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yke2n6m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http